### LWA Backend Engines — HTTP request collection
###
### Compatible with VS Code REST Client, JetBrains HTTP Client, and Postman
### (paste each block as a separate request). All requests are read-only or
### deterministic local demos. No payouts, no posting, no paid providers.
###
### Set the target by changing the @host variable below.

@host = http://localhost:8000


### Registry — list all 10 engines
GET {{host}}/engines
Accept: application/json


### Roll-up health — healthy_count / count and per-engine status
GET {{host}}/engines/health
Accept: application/json


### Engine detail — operator_admin (the read-only roll-up engine)
GET {{host}}/engines/operator_admin
Accept: application/json


### Engine detail — brain
GET {{host}}/engines/brain
Accept: application/json


### Engine detail — render
GET {{host}}/engines/render
Accept: application/json


### Demo — creator (source ingest, mission seed)
POST {{host}}/engines/creator/demo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "demo source",
  "title": "Demo upload"
}


### Demo — brain (signal ranking, recommended action)
POST {{host}}/engines/brain/demo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recommended_action": "Lead with the strongest hook"
}


### Demo — render (strategy-only fallback proof)
POST {{host}}/engines/render/demo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "render_requested": false
}


### Demo — marketplace (teaser only)
POST {{host}}/engines/marketplace/demo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "preview_offer": "Creator growth lane"
}


### Demo — wallet_entitlements (no payouts)
POST {{host}}/engines/wallet_entitlements/demo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "credits": 120
}


### Demo — proof_history (demo proof record)
POST {{host}}/engines/proof_history/demo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "proof_id": "proof_demo_001"
}


### Demo — world_game (Signal Sprint mission)
POST {{host}}/engines/world_game/demo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current_realm": "signal_realm"
}


### Demo — safety (claim/payout guard)
POST {{host}}/engines/safety/demo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "request_type": "clip_review"
}


### Demo — safety BLOCKED path (payout request must be denied)
POST {{host}}/engines/safety/demo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "request_type": "payout"
}


### Demo — social_distribution (no external posting)
POST {{host}}/engines/social_distribution/demo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "destination": "manual_review"
}


### Demo — operator_admin (read-only system snapshot)
POST {{host}}/engines/operator_admin/demo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "focus": "investor_demo"
}


### --- Single-engine Railway service routes ---
### Each per-engine Railway service has a different host and serves
### exactly one engine, chosen by LWA_ENGINE_SERVICE_ID env var.

@engine_host = http://localhost:8001


### Engine service — banner + selection
GET {{engine_host}}/
Accept: application/json


### Engine service — liveness (never raises)
GET {{engine_host}}/health
Accept: application/json


### Engine service — selected engine record
GET {{engine_host}}/engine
Accept: application/json


### Engine service — selected engine health
GET {{engine_host}}/engine/health
Accept: application/json


### Engine service — selected engine demo run
POST {{engine_host}}/engine/demo
Content-Type: application/json

{}
